notes_about_cleaning: Fields are anchored on meaningful value cells (inputs, calculations, outputs) and merge nearby label/unit/constraint cells.
Trivial operator cells (e.g., a standalone "=") are not emitted as fields.
For key outputs (e.g., N22), dependency trees are included to explain how upstream inputs drive the result.

fields.name: Axial/Bending Utilization
fields.explanation: Selects the appropriate utilization demand/capacity interaction value based on member type (F16) and whether axial force is compression or tension (F39). For Axial-Bending + Compression it returns G125; for Axial-Bending + Tension it returns G127; otherwise "N/A".
